# UI audit — host side. Sits in lobby/match/summary so we get a
# clean screenshot of each at the default 1280x720. Pairs with the
# client to populate a 2-player lobby.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/ui_host
network host 24021
name HostA

at  60 shot lobby_2p
at 200 shot match
at 750 shot summary
at 800 end
